song.title: Stilla Natt (Silent Night) - Caustic Robot Version
song.info:
Christmas song with a robot singing the swedish lyrics of Silent Night.
Made in the smartphone DAW Caustic 3.2.
Inside look of the music can be seen here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EiBrJ1mFJ04
This version has a post limiter applied to the audio, which makes it sound a bit louder than in the Youtube video.
